[telegram] <Regnar> Nope. Also if you have multiple addresses where you are holding KMD I wouldn't consolidate vote tokens before voting (meaning sending vote to a single address to actually vote from). You can consolidate KMD before the airdrop to get all your vote tokens in the same address.
